**Example Update Request**:

`PATCH <domain>/eox-tenant/api/v1/microsites/xAer5z6FEbW/`

    body: {
        "values": {
            "Test": "these are the new values."
        }
    }

    Response:
    {
        "id": 1001,
        "values": {
            "test": "new values"
        },
        "key": "xAer5z6FEbW",
        "subdomain": "testing.site-1.localhost",
        "organizations": []
